[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 6.32,
    "text": "Hey guys, it's Shane from English Understood here, and this is part three of the pronunciation tip series."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.88,
    "endTime": 8.06,
    "text": "Izeegoing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.06,
    "endTime": 9.18,
    "text": "Izithere?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.18,
    "endTime": 12.32,
    "text": "Huh!? What's 'izee'? What's 'izit'?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.32,
    "endTime": 17.52,
    "text": "'Izee' is how we say 'is he' very, very quickly. Izee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.94,
    "endTime": 21.12,
    "text": "And when you say this, it is a voiced sound."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.12,
    "endTime": 26.200000000000003,
    "text": "So your throat must be vibrating. Izee. Izee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.32,
    "endTime": 32.659,
    "text": "And 'izit' is what 'is it' sounds like when it's said very, very quickly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.864,
    "endTime": 34.352,
    "text": "Izit. Izit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.66,
    "endTime": 38.019,
    "text": "And when we say this, your throat must vibrate again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.06,
    "endTime": 41.22,
    "text": "It's a voiced sound. So now you try."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.22,
    "endTime": 43.56,
    "text": "Izee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.9,
    "endTime": 45.879,
    "text": "Izit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.14,
    "endTime": 55.06,
    "text": "When we say 'is' and we have a word after 'is', which starts with a vowel, normally we can join those two words together."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.22,
    "endTime": 59.019,
    "text": "For example, izadamgoing? Izadamgoing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.3,
    "endTime": 62.22,
    "text": "This means: Is Adam going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.368,
    "endTime": 66.0,
    "text": "Izamerica a big country? Izamerica a big country?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.44,
    "endTime": 69.3,
    "text": "Is America a big country?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.488,
    "endTime": 71.168,
    "text": "Izoceans Eleven a good movie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.728,
    "endTime": 73.472,
    "text": "Izoceans Eleven a good movie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.98,
    "endTime": 77.75,
    "text": "Is 'Ocean's Eleven' a good movie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.75,
    "endTime": 81.68,
    "text": "Just remember, when you say this, the sound must be voiced."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.12,
    "endTime": 84.44,
    "text": "Your throat must vibrate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.72,
    "endTime": 86.44,
    "text": "Izee. Izee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.84,
    "endTime": 91.02000000000001,
    "text": "But if you don't make your throat vibrate, it will sound like this:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.18,
    "endTime": 92.56,
    "text": "Issy. Issy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.56,
    "endTime": 95.78,
    "text": "And 'issy' isn't a word and doesn't really make sense."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.94,
    "endTime": 101.551,
    "text": "So try this with your native speaker friends, and they will think that you are a native speaker too."
  }
]